<plot>'Hombre's Trouble' is a short film that attempts to shed light on an iconic Seattle protester and his ongoing war against a multifaceted 'Devil Communist.' The documentary incorporates both observational and cinema verite techniques that result in an intimate portrait of Juan Torres, a Cuban refugee that came to America in 1980.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?243741</url></doc>
